        <summary>
            <![CDATA[&nbsp;]]>
        </summary>
        <description>
        	The Year End Salary Expense Transfer document is used to move salaries and staff benefit
        	charges for a given employee for a particular accounting period (or set of periods)
        	from one or more accounts to another account (or accounts). This document is used in
        	the case where an employee's payroll expense was charged to an incorrect account or object code.        	
        </description>
        
        <allowsCopy>true</allowsCopy>
        <allowsErrorCorrection>true</allowsErrorCorrection>
    </transactionalDocument>
